  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Mix kabanos with sugar and lemon juice.",
    "Stir in salt and melted butter until well combined.",
    "Fold in flour and eggs, mixing gently until batter is smooth but not overly compacted.",
